flowchart TD
    Start([Interpolation Method Selection]) --> RealTime{Is real-time<br/>processing required?}
    
    RealTime -->|Yes| Nearest[Nearest Neighbor<br/>Fast O-N complexity]
    RealTime -->|No| Uncertainty{Is uncertainty<br/>quantification needed?}
    
    Uncertainty -->|Yes| SignalType1{Is signal<br/>smooth?}
    SignalType1 -->|Yes| GaussianKDE[Gaussian KDE<br/>Natural uncertainty]
    SignalType1 -->|No| RBF[RBF<br/>Exact interpolation]
    
    Uncertainty -->|No| Sparse{Is data sparse<br/>&lt;1 point per voxel?}
    
    Sparse -->|Yes| SparseMethod{Choose method}
    SparseMethod -->|IDW| IDW[IDW Interpolation<br/>Distance-weighted]
    SparseMethod -->|KDE| GaussianKDE
    
    Sparse -->|No| Smooth{Is signal smooth<br/>temperature, density?}
    
    Smooth -->|Yes| SmoothMethod{Choose method}
    SmoothMethod -->|Gaussian| GaussianKDE
    SmoothMethod -->|Linear| Linear[Linear Interpolation<br/>k-nearest neighbors]
    
    Smooth -->|No| Sharp{Are sharp features<br/>important?}
    
    Sharp -->|Yes| SharpMethod{Choose method}
    SharpMethod -->|Nearest| Nearest
    SharpMethod -->|IDW| IDW
    
    Sharp -->|No| DefaultMethod{Choose method}
    DefaultMethod -->|Linear| Linear
    DefaultMethod -->|Gaussian| GaussianKDE
    
    Nearest --> End([Selected Method])
    IDW --> End
    Linear --> End
    GaussianKDE --> End
    RBF --> End
    
